F-Droid users can wait for the update from F-Droid, which usually arrives within a few hours with the IzzyOnDroid repo, and a few days with F-Droid.org\'s repo.
When an update is available, you will be asked if you want to install it. There won\'t be automated installs, behind your back.
But these updates would not go through the additional screening performed at e.g. IzzyOnDroid or F-Droid.
